tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_reports (
    report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    report_date TIMESTAMP,
    patient_id UUID,
    outcome_score INT,
    trend VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_outcomes (
  report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id UUID,
  therapist_id UUID,
  session_date DATE,
  session_duration INTERVAL,
  session_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_trends (
  trend_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  trend_date DATE,
  trend_category TEXT,
  trend_value FLOAT,
  trend_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE treatments (
	treatment_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
	patient_id INT REFERENCES patients(patient_id),
	treatment_type VARCHAR(50),
	start_date DATE,
	end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    psychiatrist_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    outcome TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_appointments (
  appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  appointment_date TIMESTAMP,
  appointment_type VARCHAR(20),
  diagnosis VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  appointment_id INT,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  session_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE telepsychiatry_reports (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id INT,
  report_date DATE,
  report_type VARCHAR(50),
  outcome VARCHAR(100)
);
